PointAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order to use ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"’s methods. Do not create instances of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly, and do not create your own subclasses of this class. The shape","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"classes correspond to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Geometry","type":"text"},{"text":" object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"types in the GeoJSON standard, but some have nonstandard names for backwards","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"compatibility.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Although you do not create instances of this class directly, yo